text: Mosonmagyaróvári Torna Egylet are a Hungarian association football club from the town of Mosonmagyaróvár. ==History== Mosonmagyaróvári TE debuted in the 2016–17 Nemzeti Bajnokság II season of the Hungarian League. ==Managers== József Király == References == ==External links== * Official website of the club * Profile on Magyar Futball Category:Football clubs in Hungary Category:1904 establishments in Hungary Category:Association football clubs established in 1904
